<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>User</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.5.1.slim.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/popper.js@1.16.1/dist/umd/popper.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>

    <style>
        .bg-darkblue {
            background-color: #121b27;
        }

        .navbar-transparent {
            background-color: white;
        }

        .vertical-buttons {
            position: absolute;
            top: 50%;
            right: 30px;
            transform: translateY(-50%);
            background-color: #ffffff; /* White */
            padding: 70px;
            border-radius: 10px;
        }

        .vertical-buttons .btn {
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            padding: 30px;
            background-color: #1c5392; /* Dark blue */
            color: #ffffff; /* White */
            border: none;
        }

        .vertical-buttons .btn:hover {
            background-color: #549bb3; /* Dark blue (hover) */
            color: #fff; /* White (hover) */
        }

        .navbar-nav .nav-item .btn {
            background-color: #1f5485; /* Dark blue */
            border-color: #1f5485; /* Dark blue */
            color: #ffffff; /* White */
        }

        .navbar-nav .nav-item .btn:hover {
            background-color: #538fa3; /* Dark blue (hover) */
            border-color: #265b6d; /* Dark blue (hover) */
            color: #fff; /* White (hover) */
        }

        .navbar-brand img {
            width: 110px;
            height: auto;
        }

        .booking-text {
            color: #fff; /* White */
            font-size: 20px;
            max-width: 400px;
            margin-left: auto;
            margin-right: auto;
            padding: 20px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            text-align: center; /* Center align text */
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .vertical-buttons {
                right: 10px;
                top: auto;
                bottom: 20px;
                transform: translateY(0%);
                padding: 20px;
            }

            .vertical-buttons .btn {
                padding: 20px;
            }

            .booking-text {
                max-width: 100%;
                padding: 20px;
                font-size: 16px;
                margin-left: 0;
                text-align: center;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body class="bg-darkblue">
    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-light bg-light navbar-transparent">
        <div class="container">
            <a class="navbar-brand" href="#">
                <img src="logo.png" alt="Logo">
            </a>
            <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#navbarNav"
                aria-controls="navbarNav" aria-expanded="false" aria-label="Toggle navigation">
                <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
            </button>
            <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarNav">
                <ul class="navbar-nav ml-auto d-flex">
                    <li class="nav-item flex-fill mr-2">
                        <a class="btn btn-dark px-4 py-2 btn-block" href="/">Home</a>
                    </li>
                    <!-- Added the Help button -->
                    <li class="nav-item flex-fill mr-2">
                        <a class="btn btn-dark px-4 py-2 btn-block" href="#">Help</a>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>


    <div class="booking-text">
        <p>At SkyReserve, we're dedicated to providing you with an unparalleled booking experience for your next
            adventure.
            With our user-friendly platform, extensive flight options, and secure payment system, booking your flights
            has
            never been easier. Whether you're jetting off for a relaxing vacation or embarking on a business trip, trust
            SkyReserve to handle all your flight arrangements with efficiency and care.</p>
    </div>
</body>

</html>
